\n< Male >...I'm going to remove the blindfold and
handcuffs now. Don't struggle. You'll
only end up hurting yourself.

\n< Male >Oh, if you put it that way, it's like the
backstage of a product. The items to be
exhibited are placed here just before
being displayed.
\n< Male >In other words, it's your turn next.

\n< Serena >...In this auction, it seems that even
unicorns are being listed for sale. Have
they already been sold?

\n< Male >What's the point of asking such a thing? It's
none of your business. You should worry
about your own future.

\n< Male >I hope you at least get to be owned by a
decent rich person and live until you
become an adult, okay?

\n< Serena >If only I had brought the ring with me...
I could quickly get out of this cage and
search for that child...

\n< Serena >Cecilia's plan is currently progressing in the
worst-case scenario. Even if I could
equip the ring on the altar, I wonder if
it would really...

\n< Serena >Applause and cheers... Does that mean the item
has been sold? In other words, is it my
turn next...?

\n< Serena >Ugh... My mouth is dry... My nose feels
tingly...

\n< Male >It's your turn, brat. Change your body at
the end.

\n< Male >Open your mouth. Move your tongue. Up,
right, left.

\n< Male >Show me your ears. Open your fingers.
Armpits. No problem.

\n< Male >The bidding will begin for you. The
customers need to see every inch of your
body.

\n< Male >Besides, you don't need clothes anymore. From
now on, being naked is your formal
attire.

\n< Male >Well, it depends on the preferences of Master
though.

\n< Serena >Th-the...situation...what should I do...what should I do, what
should I do.

\n< Male >Ah, a unicorn has been brought in. Its turn
is next for you. In other words, you are
the opening act.

\n< Male >Let me give you a glimpse before you leave.
This will be the last stroke of luck in
your life, after all.

\n< Serena >(Luck... Is this the last stroke of luck in my
life?)

\n< Serena >(Ah, it's fine. If it's such good luck, I
don't care if it's the last thing in my
life...!)

\n< Serena >(Oh, Splendour! You, whom I have been
searching for so long, are now so
close...!)

\n< Serena >(Finally... I found the location! I found where it
is! All that's left is to go up on
stage, receive the ring from Lady
Cecilia, and come back here!)

\n< Serena >(There is no longer any hesitation or fear.
Courage wells up from the depths of my
heart.)

\n< Serena >(...Just a little more. Just a little more
patience. I will definitely come to
rescue you, Splendour...! I will hold
you in my arms once again...!)

\n< Male >...Hmm. Ah, I hear you. I understand the
preparations.
\n< Male >Hey kid, it's finally your turn.
\n< Male >Rejoice. Your bid is a special order.

\n< Male >Please do your best to liven up the atmosphere
and warm up the place, okay?

\n< Serena >...Hmph. I don't care what it is. You can do
whatever you want.

\n< Serena >I will endure any humiliation. Right now,
I am not afraid of anything.

\n< Cecilia >Just to make sure, do you understand the
structure of the fortress? And the
directions to get outside...

\n< Serena >I apologize, I was brought here
blindfolded...

\n< Cecilia >Damn it... Argh...! I guess I have no choice
but to lead the way...!

\n< Cecilia >Alright, I'll dash ahead, but more than half of
it is a maze, so don't complain if we
hit a dead end!

\n< Serena >Understood, I will trust you, Cecilia, and follow
along.

\n< Male >Hurry up and go to the auction venue on the
south side. If you're scared, I can give
you some time to pray to the goddess
statue.
\n< Serena >...Going back there now is like going to die.
\n< Cecilia >Where are you going?! Hurry up! Over here!
